1, 2014, NET INCOME ATTRIBUTABLE TO NONCONTROLLING INTEREST WAS SIGNIFICANTLY REDUCED. THE PRIMARY REMAINING NONCONTROLLING INTEREST RELATES TO 3M INDIA LIMITED, OF WHICH 3M’S EFFECTIVE OWNERSHIP IS 75 PERCENT.

